OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1778861473
OL,3,C#139 million paid out in Troubles
OL,4,Cdisablement pension scheme
OL,6,FSome #139 million has been paid out so
OL,7,Ffar in a scheme for those permanently
OL,8,Fdisabled in an incident from Northern
OL,9,FIreland's troubled past.
OL,11,FThe total comes just months before the
OL,12,FTroubles Permanent Disablement Payment
OL,13,FScheme will close to new applicants at
OL,14,Fthe end of August.
OL,16,FIt opened on August 31, 2021 with the
OL,17,Faim of providing those living with a
OL,18,Fdisablement through no fault of their
OL,19,Fown in the Troubles with a payment in
OL,20,Frecognition of the harm they suffered,
OL,21,Fand impact on their carers.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
