FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1778861473
OL,3,C#139 million paid out in Troubles
OL,4,Cdisablement pension scheme
OL,6,FThe scheme, administered by the
OL,7,FVictims' Payments Board (VPB), can
OL,8,Faward payments ranging from #2,494 to
OL,9,F#12,471 per annum to those eligible.
OL,11,FThe leaders of the VPB appeared before
OL,12,Fthe Executive Office committee on
OL,13,FWednesday.
OL,15,FVPB secretary Paul Bullick told MLAs
OL,16,Fthat as of this week, around #139
OL,17,Fmillion has been paid to eligible
OL,18,Fapplicants.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1778861473
OL,3,C#139 million paid out in Troubles
OL,4,Cdisablement pension scheme
OL,6,FHe said they have received just over
OL,7,F13,000 applications to the scheme,
OL,8,Fincluding around 950 from applicants
OL,9,Foutside of Northern Ireland, and that
OL,10,Fthey expect a small spike before the
OL,11,Fscheme closes.
OL,13,FVPB president Mr Justice McAlinden
OL,14,Fhighlighted that they have received a
OL,15,Flimited number of applications from
OL,16,Fveterans.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1778861473
OL,3,C#139 million paid out in Troubles
OL,4,Cdisablement pension scheme
OL,6,F"We're certainly making every effort
OL,7,Fto ensure through contact with
OL,8,Fveterans' organisations that people do
OL,9,Fnot feel put off making applications,
OL,10,Fthat the scheme is for them as well,"
OL,11,Fhe said.
OL,13,F"There are issues in relation to the
OL,14,Fdeductions from other payments, etc,
OL,15,Fwe'll face those issues but we always
OL,16,Fhave to address every issue under the
OL,17,Fscheme in a victim-centric manner,
OL,18,Fwith a victim-centric focus."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@eO]uD@AOUzD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1778861473
OL,3,C#139 million paid out in Troubles
OL,4,Cdisablement pension scheme
OL,6,FMr Bullick went on to outline that
OL,7,Faround 6,000 applications were listed
OL,8,Ffor consideration in front of a panel,
OL,9,Fand to date some 4,800 determinations
OL,10,Fhave been made, with around 3,000
OL,11,Fbeing found to be eligible, and 1,800
OL,12,Ffound ineligible.
OL,14,F"With the scheme due to close for
OL,15,Fapplications in August this year, we
OL,16,Fhave continued to work with our media
OL,17,Fpartners to ensure that the messaging
OL,18,Fis pushed to as wide an audience as
OL,19,Fpossible, particularly in wider Great
OL,20,FBritain, the Republic of Ireland and
OL,21,Ffurther afield," he said.
OL,26,@vD@AOU}D@PO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1778861473
OL,3,C#139 million paid out in Troubles
OL,4,Cdisablement pension scheme
OL,6,F"An awareness campaign did take place
OL,7,Fin September 2025 to advertise the
OL,8,Fscheme across a wide range of
OL,9,Fstakeholders, political
OL,10,Frepresentatives and welfare groups
OL,11,Fthroughout the UK, Republic of Ireland
OL,12,Fand further afield."
OL,14,FHe added: "It shouldn't be
OL,15,Funderestimated the difference that
OL,16,Fthis scheme has made to victims and
OL,17,Ftheir families. We know it has changed
OL,18,Ftheir lives for the better ` those who
OL,19,Fhave received a payment ` and provided
OL,20,Fthem with much needed support and
OL,21,Ffinancial security."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@TO]vD@KOU}D@TO]
